detail.name: Gowasu
detail.effect: [On Play] Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck, reveal up to 1 <Goku Black> or up to 1 <Zamasu> and add it to your hand. Place the rest at the bottom of your deck in a random order.

detail.name: ゴワス
detail.effect: [登場時]自分のデッキの上から5枚を見て、「ゴクウブラック」か「ザマス」1枚までを公開し、手札に加える。残りをランダムにデッキの下に置く。
